The paper presents a method for event detection using low-rank methods and matrix completion. This involves techniques from machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and data structures (cs.DS). The paper also discusses the use of distance queries and algorithms for computing distances, which are relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and information theory (cs.IT).
